d any genuinely new findings into this phase (new child if warranted) rather than assuming generation 1 is superseded wholesale.\n<!-- /ANCHOR:questions -->\n\n---\n\n## RELATED DOCUMENTS\n\n- **Source backlog**: `../research/research.md` (§4 Consolidated Findings, §5 Prioritized Remediation Backlog, §6 Meta-Findings)\n- **Phase children**: See sub-folders `[0-9][0-9][0-9]-*/` for per-phase spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md\n- **Parent Spec**: `../spec.md`\n- **Graph Metadata**: See `graph-metadata.json` for `derived.last_active_child_id` pointer","lineStart":100,"lineEnd":157,"totalLines":157,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/009-research-backlog-remediation/spec.md","time":{"start":1782890363463,"end":1782890363466}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_030fabdcca58e97c016a44bf7b3a648191b81ddec605758998"}},"id":"prt_f1c8bf9fb0017CRlG8UYbFwT4V","sessionID":"ses_0e3774f05ffeAQ2wPKEyNPUx36","messageID":"msg_f1c8baf700011qLTbJdO6Q7AIB"}}
