owing lines 35-74 of 81. Use offset=75 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"`[x]` complete, `[ ]` pending.\n<!-- /ANCHOR:notation -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-1 -->\n## Phase 1: Investigation\n\n- [ ] T001 Read `computeLineageTimeoutMs` (fanout-run.cjs:884-888) and `parseArgs` (line ~95) in full\n- [ ] T002 Write RED tests: default behavior unchanged (REQ-001); override raises ceiling (REQ-002)\n<!-- /ANCHOR:phase-1 -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-2 -->\n## Phase 2: Implementation\n\n- [ ] T003 Add `--lineage-timeout-hours <N>` CLI arg parsing\n- [ ] T004 Thread the override into `computeLineageTimeoutMs`'s ceiling computation, preserving the `iters*timeoutSeconds*2` lower-bound formula\n- [ ] T005 Document the new flag in `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md` and `.opencode/commands/deep/review.md`","truncated":true,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/009-research-backlog-remediation/002-fanout-timeout-override/tasks.md","text":"`[x]` complete, `[ ]` pending.\n<!-- /ANCHOR:notation -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-1 -->\n## Phase 1: Investigation\n\n- [ ] T001 Read `computeLineageTimeoutMs` (fanout-run.cjs:884-888) and `parseArgs` (line ~95) in full\n- [ ] T002 Write RED tests: default behavior unchanged (REQ-001); override raises ceiling (REQ-002)\n<!-- /ANCHOR:phase-1 -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-2 -->\n## Phase 2: Implementation\n\n- [ ] T003 Add `--lineage-timeout-hours <N>` CLI arg parsing\n- [ ] T004 Thread the override into `computeLineageTimeoutMs`'s ceiling computation, preserving the `iters*timeoutSeconds*2` lower-bound formula\n- [ ] T005 Document the new flag in `.opencode/commands/deep/research.md` and `.opencode/commands/deep/review.md`\n<!-- /ANCHOR:phase-2 -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-3 -->\n## Phase 3: Verification\n\n- [ ] T006 Confirm T002's RED tests now pass (GREEN)\n- [ ] T007 Run the full `deep-lo