{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782891067216,"sessionID":"ses_0e3774f05ffeAQ2wPKEyNPUx36","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_Ax5ioxP7yJ1i6ABy8VytOxGy","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/gpt/iterations/iteration-013.md\n+# Iteration 13: ADR Governance Artifacts\n+\n+## Focus\n+\n+Inspect phase 003 ADR-style children and governance docs.\n+\n+## Findings\n+\n+- `003-deep-loop-workflows/002-convergence-profile-unification-adr` has a `decision-record.md`, but the broader 003 parent lists many ADR or governance-like children as complete while glob discovery found no `checklist.md` files under 003. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/003-deep-loop-workflows/002-convergence-profile-unification-adr/decision-record.md:2] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/003-deep-loop-workflows/spec.md:45]\n+- `003-cross-mode-anti-convergence-adr` is ADR-titled and Complete, but the sampled spec still has `completion_pct: 0` and no separately discovered decision record. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/003-deep-loop-workflows/003-cross-mode-anti-convergence-adr/spec.md:2] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/003-deep-loop-workflows/003-cross-mode-anti-convergence-adr/spec.md:26] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/003-deep-loop-workflows/003-cross-mode-anti-convergence-adr/spec.md:44]\n+\n+## Novelty\n+\n+newInfoRatio: 0.60. Governance drift remains live beyond status fields.\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/deep-loops/030-agent-loops-improved/research/lineages/gpt/iterations/iteration-014.md\n+# Iteration 14: Template Task Scaffolds\n+\n+## Focus\n+\n+Check Complete folders for default task content.\n+\n+## Findings\n+\n+- Multiple Complete 003 child phases still have unchecked `T001 Create project structure` task rows. [SOURCE